div.span: Namespace: prod

Backend Deployment
- Image: ahmedbest/backend-service:latest
- Replicas: 1
- Port: 5000
- Env: backend-config, backend-secret

Backend Service
- Type: LoadBalancer
- Port: 5000
- Selector: app: backend

Keycloak Deployment
- Image: quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:22.0.0
- Replicas: 1
- Port: 8080
- Env: keycloak-config, keycloak-secret

Keycloak Service
- Type: LoadBalancer
- Port: 8080
- Selector: app: keycloak

PostgreSQL Deployment
- Image: postgres:12
- Replicas: 1
- Storage: keycloak-data PVC
- Env: keycloak-db-config, keycloak-db-secret

PostgreSQL Service
- Type: ClusterIP
- Port: 5432
- Selector: app: keycloak-db

MySQL Deployment
- Image: mysql:latest
- Replicas: 1
- Storage: db-data PVC
- Env: mysql-config, mysql-secret

MySQL Service
- Type: ClusterIP
- Port: 3306
- Selector: app: mysql

Configure Keycloak Job
- Image: ahmedbest/configure-keycloak:latest
- Command: node configure-keycloak.js
- Env: keycloak-config, keycloak-secret
